'''天主教奧茨胡恩教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Oudtshoornensis}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Diocese of Oudtshoorn}}）是[[南非|南非]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教開普敦總教區|開普敦總教區]]。

==歷史==
教區的前身是'''中好望角宗座監牧區'''，1874年8月3日成立，1939年6月13日易名，1948年12月9日升為宗座代牧區，1951年1月11日升為教區<ref>{{cite book |title=APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XVIII |year=1951 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=257-263 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-43-1951-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329082908/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-43-1951-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-29 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==現況==
教區管轄[[東開普省|東開普省]]西南部、[[西開普省|西開普省]]東南部和[[北開普省|北開普省]]南部，2004年時有26,344名教友（佔轄區總人口2.6%）、十七個堂區和十九名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-de|諾埃爾·安德肋·魯卡素|Noel Andrew Rucastle}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/04/200504a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504120800/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/04/200504a.html |archivedate=2020-05-04 |language=en |date=2020-05-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|愛德華·羅勃·亞當斯|Edward Robert Adams}}和{{link-de|方濟各·福多那督·德戈韋亞|Francisco Fortunato de Gouveia}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 28.05.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/05/28/0348/00793.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-05-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504144841/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/05/28/0348/00793.html |archivedate=2020-05-04 |language=it |date=2010-05-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 02.07.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/07/02/180702b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504140831/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/07/02/180702b.html |archivedate=2020-05-04 |language=en |date=2018-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

